General.Name: Austchina Holdings Ltd
General.Description: AustChina Holdings Limited engages in the exploration of coal properties in Australia. It holds 100% interests in two coal exploration permits, including the Barcoo River-Blackall Rail and Blackall South Corner Coal projects located in Central Queensland. The company was formerly known as Coalbank Limited and changed its name to AustChina Holdings Limited in August 2017. AustChina Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
